quran[56]{c,v,t}:
  74,1,Aey kapra orhnay waly
  74,2,Khara ho ja aur agah ker day
  74,3,Aur apney rab hi ki baraiyan biyan ker
  74,4,Apney kapron ko pak rakha ker
  74,5,Na paki ko chor day
  74,6,Aur ahsan ker kay ziyada lynay ki khuwaish na ker
  74,7,Aur apney rab ki rah mein sabar ker
  74,8,Pus jab kay sor mein phonk mari jaey gi
  74,9,To wo din bara sakht din hoga
  74,10,(jo) Kafiron per asan na hoga
  74,11,Mujhy aur usay chor day jissy mein ney akela paida kiya hay
  74,12,Aur issy bohat sa maal dy rakha hay
  74,13,Aur hazir bash ferzand bhi
  74,14,Aur mein ney ussy bohat kushadigi dy rakhi hay
  74,15,Phir bhi uski chahat hay kay mein usy or ziyada don
  74,16,Nahi nahi wo hamari ayaton ka mukhalif hy
  74,17,an qareeb mein usy ik sakht charhai charhaon ga
  74,18,Us ney ghor ker kay tajweez ki
  74,19,Usy halakat ho kaisi(tajweez)sochi
  74,20,Wo phir gharat ho kis tarah andaza kiya
  74,21,Us ney phir dekha
  74,22,Phir teweri char hai or mun banaya
  74,23,Phir pechay hat gaya aur ghoroor kiya
  74,24,Aur khynay laga yeh to sirf jado hay jo naqal kiya jata hay
  74,25,Siwaey insani kalam kay kuch bhi nahi
  74,26,Mein anqareeb usy dfozakh mein dalon ga
  74,27,aur tujhay kiya khaber kay dozakh kiya chez hay
  74,28,Na wo baqi rakhti hay aur na chorti hay
  74,29,Khal ko jholsa dyti hay
  74,30,Aur is mein unnees(19)(farshtay mukarrar) hein
  74,31,Hum ney dozakh kay daroghy say farishtay rakhein hein aur hum ney unki tadad sirf kafiron ki azmaish kay liye mukarrar ki hay takay ahl e kitab yaqeen ker lein.aur ahl e eman kay eman mein asafa ho jay aur ahl e kitab aur ahl e eman shak na kerien aur jin kay dilon mein bimari hay wo aur kafir kahein kay is biyan say Allah Talah jissy chata hay ghumrah kerta hay aur jissy chata hay hidayat dyta hay tery rab kay lashkaron ko us kay siwa koi nahi janta yeh to kul bani adam kay liye sar a sar pind o nasehat hay
  74,32,Sach khyta hon qasam hay chand ki
  74,33,Aur rat ki jab wo pechay hatay
  74,34,Aur subha ki jab kay roshan hojaey
  74,35,Kay (yaqeenan wo jahanum)bari chezon mein say ik hay
  74,36,Bani adam ko daraney wali
  74,37,(yani)ussayn jo tum mein say agay barhna chaey ya pechay hanta chaey
  74,38,Her shaks apney amal kay badlay mein girwi hay
  74,39,Magar daein hath walay
  74,40,Kay wo baheshton mein (bethay hoy)gunehgaron say
  74,41,Sawal kertay hongay
  74,42,Tumhein dozakh mein kis chez ney dala
  74,43,Wo jawab deingay kay hum namazi na thy
  74,44,Na miskeeno ko khana khilatay thy
  74,45,Aur hum bhas kernay waly(inkarion )ka sath dy ker bhas mubahisa mein mashghol raha kertay thy
  74,46,Aur roz e jaza ko jhutlatay thy
  74,47,Yahan tak kay humein mot agai
  74,48,Pus inhein sifarish kernay walon ki sifarish nafa na dy gi
  74,49,Inhein kiya hogaya hay?kay nasehat say mun mor rahy hein
  74,50,Goya kay wo bidkay hoy gadhay hein
  74,51,Jo sher say bhagaein hon
  74,52,Balkay in mein say her shaks chata hay kay usay kholi hoi kitabein di jaein
  74,53,Hergiz asa nahi (hosakta balkay)yeh qiyamat say bay khof hein
  74,54,sachi bat to yeh hay kay yeh(quran)ik nasehat hay
  74,55,Ab jo chahey issy nasehat hasil kery
  74,56,Aur wo us waqat nasehat hasil kerein gay jab Allah Talah chahein wo issi laiq hein kay issy darein aur iss laiq bhi kay wo bakhshy